â€œI was pleasantly surprised by this strain. â€œTangerine Power is an interesting mix of sweet blueberry flavors with a mild overtone of citrus/pine.  She mellows out really nice in the vape and becomes very sweet and candy like. â€œThe smell is amazing. The buds were dense and broke into tiny balls when not using a grinder. Taste is spot on with its name.â€
